messages.messageBody:
One last reminder that the Early Bird Deadline for conference
registration ends today!

You also *must* receive a coupon for a funshop prior to registering, as
were are not set up to provide coupons after-the-fact.

So get your funshop requests in *before* you register!

You do not have to register *and* pay for meals *and* pay for lodging
all today. As long as it's all covered by July 31, that's fine. But to
save with the Early Bird registration, you only have a few more hours!

As of 9:00 this morning, we already have 111 families registered! MANY
of them (more than half!) are new! It will be very exciting with all
these new faces!


~Kelly

Kelly Lovejoy
Conference Coordinator
Live and Learn Unschooling Conference
http://www.LiveandLearnConference.org
